---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="About CryptoVibe - Your trusted source for cryptocurrency insights and analysis."
>
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-12 sm:px-6 sm:py-16">
    <h1 class="mb-6 text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">About CryptoVibe</h1>

    <div class="space-y-6 text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
      <p class="text-lg">
        CryptoVibe is your trusted source for cryptocurrency news, in-depth analysis, and educational content. We help you navigate the rapidly evolving world of digital assets with clarity and confidence.
      </p>

      <p>
        Our team of experienced analysts and writers covers everything from breaking market news to deep technical analyses and beginner-friendly knowledge articles. Whether you are a seasoned trader or just starting your crypto journey, CryptoVibe has the insights you need.
      </p>

      <h2 class="pt-4 text-2xl font-bold text-text-primary">What We Cover</h2>

      <ul class="list-inside list-disc space-y-2">
        <li><span class="font-semibold text-badge-news">News</span> - Breaking developments, regulatory updates, and market-moving events in the cryptocurrency space.</li>
        <li><span class="font-semibold text-badge-knowledge">Knowledge</span> - Educational content covering blockchain fundamentals, DeFi protocols, wallet security, and more.</li>
        <li><span class="font-semibold text-badge-analysis">Analysis</span> - Technical and fundamental analysis of major cryptocurrencies and emerging projects.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="pt-4 text-2xl font-bold text-text-primary">Our Mission</h2>

      <p>
        We believe that access to quality information is the foundation of smart investing. Our mission is to cut through the noise and deliver actionable insights that empower our readers to make informed decisions in the crypto market.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
